org.joda.primitives.list.impl

Class ImmutableArrayBooleanList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.joda.primitives.collection.impl.AbstractPrimitiveCollectable<Boolean>
      • org.joda.primitives.collection.impl.AbstractBooleanCollection
        • org.joda.primitives.list.impl.AbstractBooleanList
          • org.joda.primitives.list.impl.ImmutableArrayBooleanList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Boolean>, Collection<Boolean>, List<Boolean>, BooleanCollection, PrimitiveCollection<Boolean>, BooleanIterable, BooleanList, PrimitiveList<Boolean>, PrimitiveCollectable<Boolean>

    public final class ImmutableArrayBooleanList
extends AbstractBooleanList
    Immutable array-based implementation of BooleanList for primitive int elements.

    This class implements List allowing seamless integration with other APIs.

    Add, Remove, Set and Clear are not supported as this class is immutable.

    Since:
    1.0
